programme.desc: This movie is the directorial debut of actor Eric Kot for Wong Kar Wai. programme.title: Flirting Scholar from the Future
programme.desc: Tiger, Lambert and Skinny Pig are massive fans of the movie, Flirting Scholar. One day, Skinny Pig who is an obscure inventor, puts together a movie time machine and accidentally sucks all of them into the movie of Flirting Scholar. The trio head off to Wah mansion to meet the maid Autumn can they find her and can they return to the present?

programme.title: Over My Dead Body
programme.desc: This dark comedy begins with an unidentified corpse appearing at the doorstep of a residential flat. Fearing that the corpse will turn their flats into "haunted flats", which will cause a drastic drop in the property value, the four families living on the same floor attempt to move the corpse away, embroiling themselves in chaos.

programme.title: Sound of Colors
programme.desc: Lonesome marriage consultant Ming meets a blind but charming young lady, Yeuk, at a subway station. When Ming suddenly turns blind too, Yeuk helps him navigate through his world of darkness, and they begin to fall in love. This feature is based on the illustrated book from famous Taiwan illustrator Jimmy Liao.

programme.title: Wolf Hiding
programme.desc: A cold-blooded killer, Chen An vows to take revenge for her sister who was killed by a crime gang. Dealing with the police and the triad at the same time, a final battle between good and evil has just begun!

programme.title: Another Me
programme.desc: Constable Li Mao marries a rich girl but her parents disapprove of their marriage. One day, Li accidentally discovers that he looks exactly like the prince! While he aims to secure a high ranking position in the palace, the prince wants freedom, so they decide to switch identities. This however, got them both involved in the ministers conspiracy

programme.title: The Locksmith
programme.desc: Locksmith Master Shan suffers from dementia and passes on his skills to Hao Ren, who surpasses him. Detective Liu often seeks Hao Ren's help and they become good friends. When Hao Ren reunites with an old friend one day, he accidentally unfolds the truth behind Shan's wife's disappearance, leading to a chain of mysterious events.

programme.title: Where The Wind Blows
programme.desc: Founded in the 70s, Hong Kongs ICAC is committed to fight corruption in the police force. Detectives Lui Lok and Nam Kong build a corruption system that creates conflicts between the triad and the police. When ICAC hunts down the two, their control finally comes to an end. Where the wind blows, Hong Kong is no longer what it used to be!

programme.title: The Fatal Raid
programme.desc: Twenty years after a deadly bloodbath between the Hong Kong Police and Macau gangsters, Madam Fong, the surviving team member, leads a new squad of four policewomen across borders to pursue young anarchists terrorizing Macau in a mission to protect the Hong Kong Polices Deputy Chief Commissioner.

programme.title: The Movie Emperor
programme.desc: Hong Kong megastar Lau Wai Chi aspires to win a film award. He teams up with director Lin Hao to make a film about rural China so as to win at the international film festival, and experiences local village life for the farmers role. This ends up in a series of hilarious events instead.

programme.title: Chinese Odyssey 2002
programme.desc: Set in Ming Dynasty, young Emperor Zheng De escapes from the palace with his sister who disguised as a man. They run into a notorious wanderer who runs a restaurant with his boyish sister in Jiang Nan. The two pairs of siblings from vastly different social classes descend into an inescapable swirl of gender confusion, slapstick antics and love.

programme.title: The Lady Iron Chef
programme.desc: Beer girl and part-time model Ceci has terrible cooking skills. Coming from a well-off family that owns a big culinary business, wealthy SK meets Ceci in a gourmet competition held by his family's company. Despite their different backgrounds, Ceci and SK fall for each other. However, SK's dominating mother disapproves of their relationship. To win over her future mother-in-law, Ceci must beat her rival Jade in a gourmet showdown

programme.title: Look Up
programme.desc: This film celebrates the 25th anniversary of Hong Kongs Handover in a series of four cultural stories about young Hong Kongers from different walks of life: a young man with autism pursuing his dream, a reconciliation between father and son, a Chinese opera star helping young pop singers, and a Nepali youth becoming a professional lion dancer.

programme.title: Mr. & Mrs. Player
programme.desc: Chinese Feng Shui master, Carson (Chapman To) was a "Natural Born Player", taking names and breaking hearts. Fate had it that he would meet his match, the hot veterinarian, Chi-Ling (Chrissie Chau). It was love at first sight but neither could stand the other's fickle nature lest the affair might have ended as soon as it began.

programme.title: Love After Love
programme.desc: Directed by Ann Hui, the movie is adapted from Eileen Changs first short story. Set in 1930s, Wei Long travels to Hong Kong from Shanghai to pursue her education. Struggling financially, she asks her aunt to help pay for tuition but ends up being her aunts puppet to lure rich men. When Wei Long falls for playboy, George, she sinks into a life of depravity.

programme.title: Love at First Lie
programme.desc: An ordinary, cheerful and kind-hearted girl Bao, meets a troubled rich guy Edward by chance one summer. To ruin his fathers remarriage plans, Edward hires Bao and her friend to sabotage the wedding and that is how Bao and Edward meet and fall in love. All seems well for the sweet couple until their love quickly takes an unexpected turn

programme.title: Love and Let Love!
programme.desc: Cliff proposes to his girlfriend Terry but is killed in a car accident before she says yes. Terry is devastated and inconsolable. When Cliff's ghost returns, they seem to go back to their good old days. However, Cliff is determined to help Terry get over his death and start anew.

programme.title: The Moon Thieves
programme.desc: A crooked watch dealer assembles a daring crew - a thief, an explosive expert, a lock breaker and a watch connoisseur - to steal three luxury watches in Tokyo. Their mission takes an unexpected turn when they discover the legendary 'Moonwatch.' Pursued by the yakuza, the team must unite to navigate the chaos and pull off their high-stakes heist.

programme.title: Shadows
programme.desc: Ching is a forensic psychiatrist who has the power to enter a persons subconscious mind. In her latest case, she suspects that another psychiatrist is responsible for a brutal murder-cum-suicide case involving a social worker. In the investigation process, Ching finds herself under suspicion instead, as she comes face-to-face with a past trauma

programme.title: Raging Fire
programme.desc: As the police sets to arrest a drug lord, a team of masked thugs steals the drugs and murders the cops. Inspector Bong is devastated to see the aftermath of the carnage and soon discovers that the killers are led by Ngo, a former fellow cop who was forced into a life of crime by him. As the two men meet again, it is time to settle the score

programme.title: Two Tigers
programme.desc: This crime comedy is about a bumbling young man Fang Nan, who kidnaps a middle-aged businessman Zhang Cheng Gong for ransom. However, the captor becomes the captive when Zhang turns the tables on Fang and forces him to complete three tasks. The two men soon find themselves sharing a journey filled with absurdity and deception.

programme.title: American Dreams in China
programme.desc: During the economic reform period in the 80s, three undergraduates are brought together by a common ambition to live the American dream.

programme.title: From Vegas to Macau III
programme.desc: Ken holds a wedding ceremony in Macau for his daughter Rainbow. However, an explosion during the wedding causes Rainbow to fall into coma, while Ken and his friend Mark, are accused of engulfing some illicit money. Enraged, Ken swears to seek vengeance and pursue the mastermind who has gotten them involved in his evil plan.

programme.title: Cloudy Mountain
programme.desc: When a decade-long tunnel project is about to complete, an earthquake strikes and leads to a series of subsidence and landslides. The tunnel and a nearby town are at stake. A retired soldier and his son step up to try and stop the disasters at source. Will the authority decide to blow up the tunnel to save the 160,000 people in town?

programme.title: The Way We Keep Dancing
programme.desc: This sequel of The Way We Dance features the plight of Hong Kongs grassroots performing artists as they fight against the governments plan to gentrify an industrial district where they settled in.

programme.title: Wu Xia
programme.desc: Martial artist Liu hides his identity and lives in a remote village with his wife Ah Yu and their two sons, but somehow gets embroiled in a bizarre murder case. Constable Xu is a kung fu fanatic, whose curiosity forces Liu into a death duel with the Sect Leader of the 72 Demons, and puts Lius family and homeland in a great danger...

Namun krisis pelatih yang dialami mengharuskan Donald kembali melatih timnas Indonesia untuk bertanding setelah pensiun. Kerja keras dan disiplin Donald diterapkan kepada ketiga atlet perempuan panahan itu. Hingga mereka siap diberangkatkan ke Seoul.

programme.title: Roy Kiyoshi (The Untold Story)
programme.desc: Roy, yang punya kemampuan berinteraksi dengan makhluk gaib sangat frustrasi ketika Rani adiknya diculik setan. Roy merasa gagal melindungi adiknya. Tiga tahun kemudian, Sheila, pekerja LSM yang peduli dalam penanggulangan anak hilang diteror setan ketika sedang menangani kasus anak hilang secara misterius. Sheila sangat yakin bahwa kemunculan setan ini ada hubungannya dengan kasus yang sedang ditanganinya.

programme.title: Cintaku Di Rumah Susun
programme.desc: Sebuah sketsa karikatural tetang kehidupan di rumah susun sederhana yang kehidupan penghuninya beraneka ragam. Dalam lingkungan ini terjadi persahabatan dan pertikaian antar penghuni yang penuh rahasia dan intrik

programme.title: Gentayangan
programme.desc: Abimanyu Karindra tak punya pilihan selain membawa istrinya, Sofia dan kedua anak mereka serta adiknya Sheila untuk menetap di hotel peninggalan orangtua di lembah gunung ratusan kilometer dari Jakarta, setelah dinyatakan bangkrut oleh pengadilan. Hotel Kaki Langit yang awalnya dianggap sebagai tempat tinggal yang nyaman dan tenang, berubah menjadi teror menakutkan hanya beberapa saat setelah keluarga Karindra mulai menempatinya.

programme.title: Sunti@Facebook
programme.desc: Empat mahasiswa digangu oleh kekuatan gaib setelah berteman dengan seorang gadis bernama Sunti Lara di Facebook.

programme.title: Bangkit Dari Lumpur
programme.desc: Shakira harus berhadapan dengan maut setelah tanpa sengaja menyaksikan pembunuhan yang dilakukan oleh sekelompok orang. Mayat Shakira dibuang di lumpur Sidoarjo dan jantungnya diambil untuk dijual. Setelah itu Arwah Shakira tidak tenang dan bergentayangan demi menuntut balas kepada para pelakunya

programme.title: Boneka Dari Indiana
programme.desc: Film komedi yang menceritakan tentang seorang suami, Egy, yang berada di bawah kekuasaan istrinya, Cece, yang juga di bawah mertuanya, Yudho. Namun, ada hal yang membuat Egi akhirnya memberontak dan berhenti menjadi "boneka".

programme.title: Bangkit Dari Lumpur
programme.desc: Shakira harus berhadapan dengan maut setelah tanpa sengaja menyaksikan pembunuhan yang dilakukan oleh sekelompok orang. Mayat Shakira dibuang di lumpur Sidoarjo dan jantungnya diambil untuk dijual. Setelah itu Arwah Shakira tidak tenang dan bergentayangan demi menuntut balas kepada para pelakunya

programme.title: Kutukan Arwah Santet
programme.desc: Film ini bercerita tentang kisah terbunuhnya seorang gadis yang menyimpan misteri. Beberapa tahun setelah kematiannya, arwah gadis ini pun kerap merasuki tubuh Kirana dan menimbulkan korban. Suatu hari, penyebab kematian gadis ini pun terkuak.

programme.title: Benyamin Musuh Bebuyutan
programme.desc: Cerita tentang dua keluarga yang telah bermusuhan dan menjadi musuh bebuyutan. Tidak hanya Jaim dan Rais saja, namun seluruh anggota keluarga masing masing saling bermusuhan.

programme.title: Arie Hanggara
programme.desc: Kisah nyata setelah warga Jakarta dihebohkan kasus meninggalnya seorang bocah 8 tahun bernama Arie Hanggara akibat penyiksaan orang tuanya.

programme.title: Berangkat
programme.desc: Kisah tiga sekawan, yakni, Jano, Joana, dan Dika yang masing-masing memiliki personality dan hobi yang berbeda. Mereka melakukan road trip ke Kawah Ijen dan dilanjutkan ke Bali. Bermodalkan VW Combi tua mereka menyusuri beberapa kota di Jawa dengan banyak cerita.

programme.title: Paku
programme.desc: Berkisah tentang Fahmi yang kehilangan istri tercintanya. Ia tidak ikhlas dan memutuskan mengunakan paku kuntilanak untuk membangkitkan istrinya lagi dari kematian. Semenjak istrinya bangkit kembali, banyak kejadian aneh yang datang. Hingga istrinya melahirkan anak perempuan yang dimana tidak sepenuhnya manusia.

programme.title: 5 Cewek Jagoan
programme.desc: Yanti yang berhasil lolos dari penculikan yang mengingini hasil temuan tunangannya menghubungi keempat kawannya yang mempunyai keahlian khusus. Berlima mereka menyelematkan tunangan, ibu dan adiknya yang disandera.

programme.title: Aach...Aku Jatuh Cinta
programme.desc: Menceritakan tentang kisah pasangan kekasih Yulia dan Rumi yang tumbuh bersama sejak kecil. Namun keadaan berubah ketika orang tua Rumi usahanya bangkrut dan Rumi meningalkan Yulia. Suatu saat mereka ditemukan kembali, namun dengan perasaan yang bimbang karena masing-masing sudah mempunyai calon pasangan hidupnya.

programme.title: Obama Anak Menteng
programme.desc: Barry Obama berusia 9 tahun ketika tiba di Menteng. Sebagai anak baru dengan latar belakang campur aduk membuatnya sulit beradaptasi. Persahabatannya dengan anak-anak tetangga, berbeda strata sosial yaitu Slamet dan Yuniardi, serta pembantunya yang banci, Turdi, membawa Barry ke berbagai pengalaman

programme.title: Selamanya
programme.desc: Aristha berjumpa dengan kekasih lamanya, Bara, di kantor polisi. Bara, yang merasa bersalah karena menjerumuskan Aristha ke dunia narkoba, berusaha keras menarik Aristha dari dunia itu

programme.title: Cewek Gokil
programme.desc: Keke bukan sembarang anak perempuan, kepalanya penuh dengan cita-cita dan keinginan. Impian Keke yang semakin dekat, tapi suatu kejadian memaksa Keke untuk merelakan mimpi yang sudah diraihnya itu

programme.title: El
programme.desc: Dafychi (Aurelie Moeremans), gadis berkepribadian ganda, tak pernah menyangka bahwa hidupnya yang monoton dan membosankan, tiba-tiba jadi lebih berwarna sejak bertemu Mario Adipati (Achmad Megantara), pengusaha muda sukses yang terkenal otoriter dan berhati dingin. Mereka berdua dipersatukan berkat Dafyna (Aurelie Moeremans), alter ego Dafychi. Mario merasa dirinya ditakdirkan untuk melengkapi bagian yang hilang dari gadis tersebut, walau mereka harus bertahan melewati rintangan yang menguji kesetiaan mereka.

programme.title: 5 Cowok Jagoan
programme.desc: Yanto adalah seorang cleaning service dari perusahaan obat ternama harus menyelamatkan kekasihnya, Dewi yang diculik oleh para segerombolan pasukan bersenjata dan profesional. Yanto meminta bantuan dari para keempat sahabatnya karena sejak kecil mereka saling berjanji untuk saling membantu apabila ada yang mengalami kesulitan. Mereka semua memiliki background berbeda-beda, Dedy adalah seorang hansip kampung, Danu seorang penipu ulung, Lilo seorang gamer dan ahli computer dan Reva seorang mantan preman. Dengan janji mereka tersebut, akhirnya Yanto dibantu keempat para sahabatnya serta seorang cewek jagoan juga bernama Debby.

programme.title: 2 Dari 3 Laki-Laki
programme.desc: Bercerita tentang kecurigaan Atik kepada suaminya, Doddy, yang dituduh selingkuh. Semua penjelasan Doddy selalu tidak dipercaya istrinya karena istrinya melihat kelakuan teman-temannya. Apalagi setelah istrinya melihat Doddy berpose mesra dengan wanita yang sebenernya ingin dinikahi oleh atasannya Doddy. Kesalapahaman ini akhirnya bisa terselesaikan setelah sang istri melihat sendiri kenyataan-kenyataannya.

programme.title: Drop Out
programme.desc: Jemi yang hampir di DO oleh kampusnya, merasa mendapatkan sebuah keajaiban saat seorang dosen muda, Lea, datang dan mengajar. Simbiosis mutualisme diantara keduanya pun terjadi. Lea memberikan pelajaran intensif dan sebagai balasannya, Jemi memberikan pengetahuan tentang masalah asmara kepada Lea.
